        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figure 6. Brahmaculus packhamiae (PDD 117311) A, B dried apothecia C detail of head of dried apothecium D hymenial surface of rehydrated apothecium, showing multiple separate apothecial cups E squash mount showing excipular cells and hairs in KOH + Melzer's reagent F ascoma in vertical section G paraphyses, asci, and ascospores H ascospores. Scale bars: 1 mm (A-C); 0.1 mm (D); 10 µm (E-H)." ;
